                    <span>I was a top-rated executive coach in a Fortune 100 company. But reading and applying the wisdom and knowledge contained in this book has taken me to an entirely new, more powerful level of coaching business owners and executives and helping them achieve dramatic breakthroughs in amazingly short periods of time.  It's clear that these authors are master practitioners of their craft.  Theirs is not an academic or psychological approach to coaching, but rather a powerful, pragmatic set of insights, experiences and applications.  Whether you are thinking about coaching as a profession, or trying to improve your management and mentoring skills, this is the single best resource you can find.</span>
                  
